he Bible has </div><div class="t m2e9 x25 h1f y2d6 ff1 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">helped bring about is . . . </div><div class="t m2ea x31 h1f y2d7 ff1 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m2eb x25 h1f y2d8 ff1 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A way in which the Bible has helped me relate better with </div><div class="t m2ec x25 h1f y2d9 ff1 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">people is . . . </div><div class="t ma2 x32 h1f y2da ff1 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUMMARY: The Song of Solomon comes from God and leads </div><div class="t m2ed x32 h1f y2db ff1 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to God. In revealing something of the tenderest ties that </div><div class="t m2ee x32 h1f y127 ff1 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">human hearts can know, Scripture elevates our souls toward </div><div class="t m2e5 x32 h1f y2dc ff1 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God and entwines our hearts more deeply with the Divine. </div><div class="t m2ef x79 h1f y2dd ff1 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">For </div><div class="t m89 x1a h11 y2de ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the first time in 70 years, the people of the Soviet Division may buy </div><div class="t m219 x79 h11 y2df ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Adventist literature again. Support our Soviet Adventist family, our </div><div class="t m2f0 x79 h11 y2e0 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">newest division, December 26. </div><div class="t m2f1 x54 h11 y2e1 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">19 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
